title: The Honest Kitchen Dehydrated Whole Grain Chicken Dog Food, 4 lb Box
description: The Honest Kitchen believes human grade, whole foods provide pets the best nutrition possible. This whole grain recipe is made with uncompromising quality control standards using real, whole food ingredients, like free range chicken, that are gently dehydrated to maintain nutrients & taste. To meet our 100% human grade standard, we use the same whole food ingredients you’d recognize in your own kitchen, and make this food in a human food facility. Just add warm water and wait three minutes for a tasty, homemade meal that you and your pets will love! *Substantiated by In-Home AAFCO Feeding Trial ABOUT THE HONEST KITCHEN Founded in 2002 as the first human grade food for pets, we believe that real, whole foods provide pets with the best nutrition possible. That’s why all our foods are made with the same quality and safety standards as people food (and with ingredients you can find in your kitchen). It’s what we call The Honest Difference, and we can’t wait for you to see the difference it makes!
